<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .header { background: #0078d4; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .footer { background: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
    .button { background: #0078d4; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Welcome aboard! We're excited to have you join our team as {{jobTitle}}.</p>
    
    <h2>Your Account Details</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Username:</strong> {{username}}</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
      <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Next Steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Check your email for login credentials</li>
      <li>Complete the onboarding checklist</li>
      <li>Set up your workspace</li>
      <li>Meet your team on {{startDate}}</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>
      <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">Access Employee Portal</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please reach out to HR at {{hrEmail}}.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    {{managerName}}<br>
    {{managerTitle}}</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2026 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
